I've been smashing it with Spectre recently. She requires a very specific strategy to be effective, but when it comes off she's a beast. Her ultimate is so good early game. You can just rack up kills and the associated gold by teleporting straight to any enemy hero unlucky enough to find themselves with low health.Race to a Vanguard and you become pretty hard to kill. Then a Diffusal Blade to massively increase the effectiveness of your ulti. Then if you can get the gold together for a Radiance your ulti will be an I Win Button.
